+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+

compose_newwindow changes the behavior of the default compose / reply /
forward buttons in the main mail list so that they open the new message in 
a separate window (or tab depending on your browser settings)


To download the file in either ZIP or TAR format go to
http://github.com/xrxca/cnw
and click on the 'Download Source' button near the top.

The zip or tar.gz file will have a xrxca-cnw-????? directory
that will contain the actual compose_newwindow plugin directory
move/copy the compose_newwindow directory to your plugins
directory and enable the plugin in your config/main.inc.php file.

